<p>Is there any solution to set default path for image sources for windows phone? Some manifest changes?</p>  <p>I want to write <code>&lt;Image Source="img1.png" /&gt;</code> instead of <code>&lt;Image Source="Assets/Images/img1.png" /&gt;</code></p>  <p>Actually this feature will be extremely useful for xamarin developers. Now I need to create such a huge piece of code in xamarin studio:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;Image&gt;         &lt;Image.Source&gt;                         &lt;OnPlatform x:TypeArguments="ImageSource"&gt;                           &lt;OnPlatform.iOS&gt;                             &lt;FileImageSource File="img1.png"/&gt;                           &lt;/OnPlatform.iOS&gt;                           &lt;OnPlatform.Android&gt;                             &lt;FileImageSource File="img1.png"/&gt;                           &lt;/OnPlatform.Android&gt;                           &lt;OnPlatform.WinPhone&gt;                             &lt;FileImageSource File="Assets/Images/img1.png"/&gt;                           &lt;/OnPlatform.WinPhone&gt;                         &lt;/OnPlatform&gt;                       &lt;/Image.Source&gt;         &lt;/Image&gt; </code></pre>  <p>And my aim is to turn this code into <code>&lt;Image Source="img1.png"/&gt;</code></p>